{"tid":144175,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個品牌硬碟最易壞？","createTime":"2017-03-05T08:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T16:46:13.000Z","uid":56533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"514be9ddda3a060d2bf83fae3aabc690a93c2b1f","tid":144175,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:16:45.000Z","msg":"雲端儲存服務商BackBlaze日前公布了最新的電腦硬碟穩定度統計，比較4大主要品牌Seagate、WDC、HGST及Toshiba產品的硬碟故障率，讓外界用作參考名評估硬碟的品質。究竟哪個品牌的表現最好？<br />\n<br />\n1. 邊個牌子故障率最低？<br />\n<br />\n綜合4大品牌多個產品的表現中，HGST為故障率最低的品牌，只得0.6%，其後依次為Toshiba、Seagate。表現最差的是WDC，故障率達3.88%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 單計2016年，哪個型號硬碟最易壞？<br />\n<br />\nBackblaze於去年365日持續使用了以下17個不同品牌的硬碟產品，雖然Seagate並非最易故障的品牌，但最易壞的硬碟則由Seagate推出的「ST4000DX000」4TB型號硬碟「一枝獨秀」奪得，以13.57% 故障率拋離其他硬碟。<br />\n<br />\n而HGST的硬碟方面，不論在8TB、4TB、3TB的硬碟產品中均屬故障率最低。<br />\n<br />\n另外，Seagate、HGST、Toshiba均有硬碟型號在全年使用中保持 0%損壞率，唯獨WDC的3款測試型號均未能在全年保持不壞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1650000/1654305/FY-2016-Drive-Failure-Rates_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1650000%2F1654305%2FFY-2016-Drive-Failure-Rates_1024.jpg&h=fa948545&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 13年至16年底，哪款硬碟故障率高達9成？<br />\n<br />\nBackblaze自13年至16年年底進行的統計中，則一共測試了 30 款硬碟型號，合共85，46個硬碟。，故障率逾10%的硬碟合共有5個，全部來自Seagate，當中故障率達90.92%的為Seagate的1.5TB「ST1500DL003」硬碟。<br />\n<br />\n雖然 Seagate 「ST8000NM0055」8TB 硬碟達到了完美的 0% 損壞率，但需留意這型號是在第四季才加入測試中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1650000/1654305/All-thru-Q4-2016-Failure-Rates_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1650000%2F1654305%2FAll-thru-Q4-2016-Failure-Rates_1024.jpg&h=21dafa47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但亦要留意，不同品牌測試的樣本數目不同，Toshiba的測試樣本遠比其他品牌少；而且有些產品屬企業級硬碟，有些產品則屬一般桌上型硬碟，可能亦對結果有所影響。但仍可供一般消費者參考。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://topick.hket.com/article/1654305/?r=mcsdfb2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1654305%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb2&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMpUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=6e45c2df\" target=\"_blank\">http://topick.hket.com/article/1654305/?r=mcsdfb2</a>"},{"pid":"67a4f2053525cfe2764fe8dc7a23563fab0fa894","tid":144175,"uid":33539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T11:52:43.000Z","msg":"死雞"},{"pid":"5f1238049d2ccd3a0f1410d2667dec77c2311b65","tid":144175,"uid":35863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:07:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死雞</blockquote><br />\n我隻seagate用咗五年都冇壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d09c975bdd447cb37413f57e6efeb96b280855","tid":144175,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:14:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>死雞</blockquote><br />\n我隻seagate用咗五年都冇壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我隻seagate過保一個月即壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bea51e342a1f0f2075df56fbcd392eeed83f01d","tid":144175,"uid":35429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:04:39.000Z","msg":"死雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193f44fc79271aa03312161fa139f75e6b9e957f","tid":144175,"uid":6860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:16:43.000Z","msg":"唉我wd red 3tb 1年半壞2次啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6ff4ac28594a51f33a5d1e1e6b3d0f3ada5483","tid":144175,"uid":18120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:18:42.000Z","msg":"當年隻死雞barracuda用左一個月就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5097372848eea4767427f3fab20964177ee24f22","tid":144175,"uid":18120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"